docs {
  # Generate OpenGraph Image
  Dynamically generates OpenGraph (OG) images for blog posts.
  
  **Route:** `GET /asset/opengraph/get`
  
  Query parameters:
  - `title`: Post title (required)
  - `slug`: Post slug for caching
  - `author`: Author name
  - `date`: Publication date
  
  Images are cached locally and regenerated if post is updated.
  Returns PNG image (1200x630px) optimized for social media.
}
